1
00:01:56,430 --> 00:01:57,840
If you don't kill it today,

2
00:01:57,840 --> 00:01:59,240
you will starve tonight.

3
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:02,950
But I can't bring myself to do it.

4
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:06,350
I can endure missing one meal.

5
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:08,150
If it's not dead by tomorrow morning,

6
00:02:08,150 --> 00:02:09,550
you will be the one to die.

7
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:18,750
See how simple it is? Take it.

8
00:02:24,630 --> 00:02:25,470
Kill it.

9
00:02:35,470 --> 00:02:38,270
Why would His Majesty
go to the General's Mansion?

10
00:02:38,470 --> 00:02:39,470
What do you think?

11
00:02:40,710 --> 00:02:44,360
I think whether His Majesty
went to the General's Mansion

12
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:47,280
or to see someone else,

13
00:02:47,870 --> 00:02:51,000
he shouldn't have sneaked out of
the palace in the middle of the night.

14
00:02:51,000 --> 00:02:52,240
As a child grows up,

15
00:02:52,240 --> 00:02:54,750
it's inevitable for him
to have distracting thoughts.

16
00:02:54,750 --> 00:02:56,430
What do you plan to do, Your Highness?

17
00:02:56,430 --> 00:02:58,030
You can't keep a child forever
when they grow up,

18
00:02:58,030 --> 00:02:59,630
let alone a younger brother.

19
00:03:02,590 --> 00:03:05,190
What matters is not what he went to do,

20
00:03:05,870 --> 00:03:07,310
but rather who, with ulterior motives,

21
00:03:07,310 --> 00:03:08,970
guided him to do these things.

22
00:03:10,870 --> 00:03:12,840
Send someone to keep an eye
on the General's Mansion.

23
00:03:12,840 --> 00:03:14,470
I want to know everyone

24
00:03:14,680 --> 00:03:16,030
who comes out of there,

25
00:03:16,030 --> 00:03:17,750
who he meets with, and what he does,

26
00:03:17,750 --> 00:03:19,710
whether it's day or night.

27
00:03:19,710 --> 00:03:20,400
Yes.

28
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,560
It's a token from the palace.

29
00:04:16,800 --> 00:04:19,160
He was the Eldest Princess's man.

30
00:04:21,160 --> 00:04:22,270
You shouldn't have killed him.

31
00:04:22,270 --> 00:04:23,390
If I hadn't killed him,

32
00:04:23,390 --> 00:04:25,950
should I have let him
go back and report to his master?

33
00:04:25,950 --> 00:04:27,160
I killed him, so what?

34
00:04:27,390 --> 00:04:28,590
Why so much nonsense?

35
00:04:29,270 --> 00:04:31,430
He followed you
from the General's Mansion to here.

36
00:04:31,430 --> 00:04:32,600
Now that he is dead,

37
00:04:33,190 --> 00:04:34,430
Liu Xie will suspect you.

38
00:04:34,430 --> 00:04:35,240
Fei Zheng,

39
00:04:35,560 --> 00:04:37,600
since when did you become so indecisive?

40
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:39,630
You weren't like this before.

41
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,600
Jinglan is not like Changmo.

42
00:04:41,600 --> 00:04:43,930
Killing someone won't solve the problem.

43
00:04:47,950 --> 00:04:49,550
When will Liu Chu come again?

44
00:04:50,070 --> 00:04:51,070
I will arrange it.

45
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:52,650
But you must promise me

46
00:04:52,950 --> 00:04:54,270
not to act rashly.

47
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,040
Are you scared?

48
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,360
If your identity is exposed

49
00:04:58,360 --> 00:04:59,760
and you fail the mission,

50
00:04:59,830 --> 00:05:01,000
you'll be punished by the Gu poison,

51
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,930
suffering a fate worse than death.

52
00:05:08,270 --> 00:05:10,470
Dispose of the body as soon as possible.

53
00:05:21,630 --> 00:05:22,480
Your Majesty.

54
00:05:27,270 --> 00:05:28,160
Your Majesty.

55
00:05:34,070 --> 00:05:35,800
Why don't you step down for now?

56
00:05:35,830 --> 00:05:36,680
Yes.

57
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:44,760
Chu, what were you
thinking about just now?

58
00:05:46,870 --> 00:05:47,870
I...

59
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:51,290
I wasn't thinking about anything.

60
00:05:52,360 --> 00:05:53,720
I thought you were thinking about

61
00:05:53,720 --> 00:05:56,050
the Princess of Changmo we met last night.

62
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:57,630
How could that be?

63
00:05:58,000 --> 00:05:59,870
She's just a princess from Changmo.

64
00:05:59,870 --> 00:06:02,270
I don't even remember what she looks like.

65
00:06:04,270 --> 00:06:06,000
You don't remember her.

66
00:06:06,430 --> 00:06:08,560
I was thinking of going again tonight.

67
00:06:09,000 --> 00:06:09,830
Let's just drop it then.

68
00:06:09,830 --> 00:06:10,750
No, no.

69
00:06:13,040 --> 00:06:14,870
Even if we don't go see her,

70
00:06:14,870 --> 00:06:15,600
we...

71
00:06:15,950 --> 00:06:17,680
can still go drink with Xiao Chi.

72
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:18,480
Right?

73
00:06:19,120 --> 00:06:20,430
Xiao Chi...

74
00:06:20,430 --> 00:06:23,030
He is getting
acupuncture treatment tonight.

75
00:06:23,190 --> 00:06:25,120
I'm afraid he can't drink with you.

76
00:06:25,750 --> 00:06:28,270
Xiao Chi's health is the top priority.

77
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:30,250
Then shouldn't we go check on him?

78
00:06:32,070 --> 00:06:34,800
What you said makes perfect sense.

79
00:06:35,070 --> 00:06:36,680
Let's go then?

80
00:06:37,360 --> 00:06:38,159
Let's go.

81
00:06:40,950 --> 00:06:43,000
Where are you going, Your Majesty?

82
00:06:43,920 --> 00:06:44,800
Your Highness.

83
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:48,159
Lord Fei and I

84
00:06:48,270 --> 00:06:51,040
were discussing some national affairs.

85
00:06:52,480 --> 00:06:55,040
I was just thinking of visiting you.

86
00:06:55,240 --> 00:06:57,240
That's exactly what I was thinking.

87
00:06:57,950 --> 00:07:00,480
I also have something to report to you.

88
00:07:03,270 --> 00:07:04,680
Lord Fei, it's so late.

89
00:07:05,120 --> 00:07:07,070
Are you planning
to stay in the palace overnight?

90
00:07:07,070 --> 00:07:07,870
So late?

91
00:07:10,680 --> 00:07:12,870
It's already... getting dark.

92
00:07:13,600 --> 00:07:14,680
Then I...

93
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:18,070
Your Highness, Your Majesty,

94
00:07:18,240 --> 00:07:20,680
I shall take my leave now.

95
00:07:24,240 --> 00:07:26,100
Your Majesty, I'll take my leave.

96
00:07:31,720 --> 00:07:32,510
Sister,

97
00:07:32,870 --> 00:07:34,240
since you came to me so late,

98
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:36,560
it must be for something very important.

99
00:07:38,560 --> 00:07:39,750
Nothing much.

100
00:07:40,270 --> 00:07:42,800
I just remembered
that the treasury ledgers

101
00:07:42,800 --> 00:07:44,260
haven't been shown to you.

102
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,630
Sister, regarding the treasury,

103
00:07:46,630 --> 00:07:48,390
I feel most at ease leaving it to you.

104
00:07:48,390 --> 00:07:50,240
Besides, I know little of ledgers.

105
00:07:50,240 --> 00:07:51,480
Why don't you just go over them yourself?

106
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,810
You shouldn't say that.

107
00:07:53,430 --> 00:07:55,070
Although we are related by blood,

108
00:07:55,070 --> 00:07:56,950
there is still a distinction
between ruler and subject.

109
00:07:56,950 --> 00:07:58,240
It is my duty.

110
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:01,480
Naturally, I must report
everything to you in detail.

111
00:08:01,870 --> 00:08:02,750
I know.

112
00:08:02,750 --> 00:08:05,390
These are all the rules
left by the late Emperor.

113
00:08:05,390 --> 00:08:08,870
But I think our bond as siblings is deep.

114
00:08:09,070 --> 00:08:10,480
You are my own sister after all.

115
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:12,160
Acting like this makes us distant.

116
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:13,040
You should just read them yourself.

117
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:13,840
Your Majesty.

118
00:08:15,040 --> 00:08:16,240
Do you

119
00:08:16,630 --> 00:08:18,490
have something else on your mind?

120
00:08:19,160 --> 00:08:20,480
How could I?

121
00:08:21,070 --> 00:08:22,360
It's so late.

122
00:08:23,240 --> 00:08:24,840
What else could be on my mind?

123
00:08:25,000 --> 00:08:27,530
If you have nothing to do,
come sit at my place.

124
00:08:28,870 --> 00:08:29,630
Wait.

125
00:08:34,080 --> 00:08:35,150
Jin Xi.

126
00:08:36,080 --> 00:08:37,870
We've been here for 2 hours.

127
00:08:37,960 --> 00:08:39,690
Who exactly are we waiting for?

128
00:08:39,750 --> 00:08:41,240
No, waiting for no one.

129
00:08:43,669 --> 00:08:47,630
Are there any changes to the plan tonight?

130
00:08:47,630 --> 00:08:48,550
What plan?

131
00:08:49,480 --> 00:08:52,030
No, nothing.

132
00:08:52,080 --> 00:08:53,210
Then I'm going back.

133
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,100
Your Highness.

134
00:08:59,550 --> 00:09:02,150
What do you think of
that man from last night?

135
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:03,360
What man?

136
00:09:03,630 --> 00:09:04,840
The man you said

137
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:06,550
fell from the sky.

138
00:09:08,670 --> 00:09:10,790
I haven't seen many men in Changmo.

139
00:09:11,270 --> 00:09:12,840
He's different from my father.

140
00:09:12,840 --> 00:09:14,840
He lacks my father's martial valor.

141
00:09:15,030 --> 00:09:16,030
That's natural.

142
00:09:16,390 --> 00:09:17,960
The King of Mo is the overlord of Changmo.

143
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,390
No man in this world

144
00:09:19,390 --> 00:09:20,450
can compare to him.

145
00:09:22,480 --> 00:09:23,440
However,

146
00:09:23,790 --> 00:09:25,250
he's not annoying either.

147
00:09:26,670 --> 00:09:27,870
Does that mean

148
00:09:28,240 --> 00:09:29,750
you like him a bit?

149
00:09:30,270 --> 00:09:31,480
How could I?

150
00:09:31,750 --> 00:09:32,480
Lord Fei,

151
00:09:32,480 --> 00:09:34,150
General Xiao, and Lieutenant Xu

152
00:09:34,150 --> 00:09:35,360
are not annoying either.

153
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:37,160
Does that mean I like all of them?

154
00:09:40,750 --> 00:09:41,600
I think

155
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:43,670
you quite like Lord Fei.

156
00:09:45,480 --> 00:09:47,840
Why do you think I like Lord Fei?

157
00:09:47,840 --> 00:09:49,080
I can't say for sure.

158
00:09:49,390 --> 00:09:52,080
It's just the way you look at him.

159
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:55,840
Your Highness, I am your wedding official.

160
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:56,840
Except for you,

161
00:09:56,840 --> 00:09:58,600
I treat everyone the same way.

162
00:09:58,870 --> 00:10:00,480
But I think you two...

163
00:10:00,480 --> 00:10:01,540
Alright, alright.

164
00:10:01,550 --> 00:10:03,280
Let me help you get back to rest.

165
00:10:04,630 --> 00:10:05,440
Okay.

166
00:10:06,030 --> 00:10:06,630
Let's go.

167
00:10:16,360 --> 00:10:18,080
What are you doing here?

168
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,120
Waiting for you.

169
00:10:19,120 --> 00:10:19,980
Waiting for me?

170
00:10:20,550 --> 00:10:22,790
I can't find you
in the General's Mansion every day.

171
00:10:22,790 --> 00:10:25,250
Do you want your condition
to flare up again?

172
00:10:25,960 --> 00:10:26,600
I...

173
00:10:26,870 --> 00:10:28,200
have been busy these days.

174
00:10:28,200 --> 00:10:29,440
I know.

175
00:10:29,440 --> 00:10:29,870
Here.

176
00:10:30,030 --> 00:10:31,490
Take this medicine first.

177
00:10:31,630 --> 00:10:33,600
Take it with this.

178
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:36,630
Now?

179
00:10:37,030 --> 00:10:37,600
Yes.

180
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,360
This is wine?

181
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,440
Its messenger herb is wine.

182
00:10:51,550 --> 00:10:52,510
Take it quickly.

183
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,890
Come back early.

184
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,030
Thank you.

185
00:11:16,240 --> 00:11:16,960
General.

186
00:11:17,150 --> 00:11:18,870
You checked the case files all night.

187
00:11:18,870 --> 00:11:20,240
Where are you going today?

188
00:11:20,240 --> 00:11:21,270
Just follow me.

189
00:11:21,390 --> 00:11:24,920
I will take you to see someone
I have respected since childhood.

190
00:11:36,200 --> 00:11:37,000
My Lord.

191
00:11:37,150 --> 00:11:38,960
You have been with me for so many years.

192
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:41,360
Don't you know my rules when reading?

193
00:11:41,360 --> 00:11:42,080
Yes.

194
00:11:42,080 --> 00:11:44,630
I know you don't like to be disturbed
while reading,

195
00:11:44,630 --> 00:11:47,790
but there are some things
I must report to you as soon as possible.

196
00:11:47,790 --> 00:11:48,960
What is it?

197
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:49,840
Spit it out.

198
00:11:50,120 --> 00:11:53,360
Xiao Chi has been checking
the Han family's case files recently.

199
00:11:53,360 --> 00:11:55,220
About the case files back then...

200
00:11:58,150 --> 00:12:01,410
This Xiao Chi is meddling in things
as soon as he comes back.

201
00:12:02,670 --> 00:12:04,440
Keep a close eye on him.

202
00:12:04,670 --> 00:12:07,440
Report to me immediately
if there is any movement.

203
00:12:07,440 --> 00:12:07,960
Yes.

204
00:12:12,630 --> 00:12:14,270
Xiao Chi.

205
00:12:26,030 --> 00:12:28,290
Sorry to keep you waiting, General Xiao.

206
00:12:28,480 --> 00:12:29,270
Lord Xue.

207
00:12:29,630 --> 00:12:30,440
Please sit.

208
00:12:34,200 --> 00:12:35,150
It's rare

209
00:12:35,150 --> 00:12:37,870
that you still remember
an old man like me.

210
00:12:38,030 --> 00:12:41,360
I've often heard of your bravery
at Tianlang Pass.

211
00:12:42,390 --> 00:12:43,790
I also heard a few days ago

212
00:12:44,150 --> 00:12:46,750
that you straightened things out
in the court.

213
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:49,150
A formidable young man indeed.

214
00:12:55,390 --> 00:12:57,870
How is your health recently, Lord Xue?

215
00:12:58,240 --> 00:12:59,550
I'm an old man now,

216
00:12:59,840 --> 00:13:02,550
so my health is definitely
not what it used to be.

217
00:13:02,840 --> 00:13:04,600
I know a physician

218
00:13:04,790 --> 00:13:06,120
with excellent medical skills.

219
00:13:06,120 --> 00:13:07,630
She can take a look at you.

220
00:13:08,150 --> 00:13:09,150
A physician?

221
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:11,150
Coincidentally,

222
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:12,960
this physician's

223
00:13:13,550 --> 00:13:14,910
surname is Han.

224
00:13:17,390 --> 00:13:20,080
Just speak your mind, General Xiao.

225
00:13:20,910 --> 00:13:21,960
I wonder if you

226
00:13:21,960 --> 00:13:24,320
still remember the Han family case?

227
00:13:26,030 --> 00:13:27,630
The Han family?

228
00:13:28,600 --> 00:13:30,790
That is an old case from years ago.

229
00:13:31,080 --> 00:13:33,080
Why bring it up suddenly?

230
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:35,150
I've been investigating this case recently

231
00:13:35,150 --> 00:13:37,480
and found many suspicious points.

232
00:13:37,480 --> 00:13:40,000
So I came to consult you.

233
00:13:40,960 --> 00:13:42,080
I see.

234
00:13:43,270 --> 00:13:45,870
However, since it is an old case,

235
00:13:46,390 --> 00:13:49,200
I don't remember it very clearly.

236
00:13:57,030 --> 00:13:58,030
Physician Han,

237
00:13:58,790 --> 00:14:01,120
I am here to get medicine
for Her Highness.

238
00:14:09,550 --> 00:14:10,550
Three times a day.

239
00:14:10,630 --> 00:14:12,430
Serve it to Her Highness on time.

240
00:14:14,480 --> 00:14:15,840
Thank you, Physician Han.

241
00:14:15,840 --> 00:14:16,790
Later,

242
00:14:16,790 --> 00:14:19,450
I will go and check on
Her Highness's condition.

243
00:14:23,240 --> 00:14:23,960
Thank you,

244
00:14:24,480 --> 00:14:25,630
Physician Han.

245
00:14:26,200 --> 00:14:26,790
Jin Xi!

246
00:14:34,030 --> 00:14:35,390
Such an erratic pulse.

247
00:14:37,870 --> 00:14:38,720
Lord Xue,

248
00:14:39,080 --> 00:14:40,440
could the Han family's case

249
00:14:40,440 --> 00:14:42,300
have been a wrongful conviction?

250
00:14:45,030 --> 00:14:46,480
The case was closed.

251
00:14:46,670 --> 00:14:49,480
Whether it was unjust or not,
it's all in the past.

252
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:51,480
General Xiao,

253
00:14:51,480 --> 00:14:53,080
let me offer you some advice.

254
00:14:53,440 --> 00:14:55,080
Don't ask what you shouldn't ask,

255
00:14:55,080 --> 00:14:56,750
and don't meddle in what you shouldn't.

256
00:14:56,750 --> 00:14:58,840
That is the way to be a good official.

257
00:15:01,670 --> 00:15:03,070
I appreciate the advice.

258
00:15:05,240 --> 00:15:07,080
Since you can't remember,

259
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,960
pardon my intrusion today.

260
00:15:10,550 --> 00:15:11,950
Take care, General Xiao.

261
00:15:12,270 --> 00:15:12,960
Farewell.

262
00:15:33,360 --> 00:15:33,890
General,

263
00:15:34,270 --> 00:15:35,750
is this the person you mentioned

264
00:15:35,750 --> 00:15:37,610
you respected in your childhood?

265
00:15:38,360 --> 00:15:39,790
I haven't seen him for many years.

266
00:15:39,790 --> 00:15:41,320
He has indeed changed a lot.

267
00:15:41,750 --> 00:15:42,790
Let's go back first

268
00:15:42,790 --> 00:15:43,650
and make plans.

269
00:15:43,670 --> 00:15:44,030
Okay.

270
00:16:02,480 --> 00:16:03,440
You're awake.

271
00:16:05,870 --> 00:16:07,510
Here, drink the medicine.

272
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,630
What's wrong with me?

273
00:16:10,870 --> 00:16:12,080
You are poisoned.

274
00:16:13,150 --> 00:16:14,200
Poisoned?

275
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:19,550
Jin Xi,

276
00:16:20,200 --> 00:16:21,510
I know who you are.

277
00:16:21,870 --> 00:16:23,150
You know who I am too.

278
00:16:24,200 --> 00:16:25,630
Since you don't want to acknowledge me,

279
00:16:25,630 --> 00:16:26,750
I won't force you.

280
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:29,420
You must have your own difficulties.

281
00:16:34,670 --> 00:16:39,670
Can you counteract this poison?

282
00:16:39,670 --> 00:16:40,670
I'm not sure.

283
00:16:41,870 --> 00:16:43,960
If you want to completely
counteract this poison,

284
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:46,670
you must tell me everything
about how you were poisoned

285
00:16:46,670 --> 00:16:48,600
and how it flared up in detail.

286
00:16:48,840 --> 00:16:50,900
Otherwise, there's nothing I can do.

287
00:16:56,600 --> 00:16:57,510
Physician Han,

288
00:16:57,510 --> 00:16:59,670
don't waste any more time on me.

289
00:16:59,750 --> 00:17:00,600
My poison

290
00:17:01,360 --> 00:17:02,510
has nothing

291
00:17:03,320 --> 00:17:04,829
to do with you.

292
00:17:04,829 --> 00:17:05,310
You...

293
00:17:10,440 --> 00:17:12,369
Better to live badly than die well.

294
00:17:12,400 --> 00:17:13,680
Only by staying alive

295
00:17:14,000 --> 00:17:15,480
can you do more things.

296
00:17:22,589 --> 00:17:24,319
I don't really want to cure you.

297
00:17:24,680 --> 00:17:25,829
I just enjoy

298
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:27,680
unraveling symptoms.

299
00:17:27,880 --> 00:17:29,830
I have nothing to do these days anyway.

300
00:17:29,830 --> 00:17:32,630
If I get an idea,
I'll prescribe you some medicine.

301
00:17:35,350 --> 00:17:37,680
Then thank you in advance, Physician Han.

302
00:17:50,550 --> 00:17:51,400
Young Master Wang,

303
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:52,830
see which one you like

304
00:17:52,830 --> 00:17:54,360
and take whatever you want.

305
00:17:56,750 --> 00:17:58,030
This stuff tastes awful.

306
00:17:58,030 --> 00:17:59,590
How dare you sell it?

307
00:17:59,750 --> 00:18:00,880
Don't! Don't!

308
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:02,030
Young Master Wang,

309
00:18:02,030 --> 00:18:04,000
I don't know which one tastes good

310
00:18:04,000 --> 00:18:05,350
or bad either.

311
00:18:05,480 --> 00:18:07,340
If you don't think it tastes good,

312
00:18:07,590 --> 00:18:09,200
how about I compensate you?

313
00:18:09,680 --> 00:18:10,750
You piece of trash.

314
00:18:11,030 --> 00:18:14,510
I am the only son
of Wang Ruhai, the Chief Minister.

315
00:18:14,830 --> 00:18:16,350
Do I care about your petty cash?

316
00:18:16,350 --> 00:18:17,880
What do you want me to do?

317
00:18:18,000 --> 00:18:19,440
Eat all of these,

318
00:18:19,830 --> 00:18:20,750
and we'll call it even.

319
00:18:20,750 --> 00:18:21,270
Ah?

320
00:18:22,350 --> 00:18:23,070
No, no!

321
00:18:23,070 --> 00:18:23,880
Feed him.

322
00:18:24,030 --> 00:18:24,790
Alright.

323
00:18:26,960 --> 00:18:28,590
Young Master Wang, please don't!

324
00:18:28,590 --> 00:18:29,650
Young Master Wang!

325
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:30,880
What are you looking at?

326
00:18:30,880 --> 00:18:32,210
Never seen this before?

327
00:18:35,030 --> 00:18:37,480
Hurry and eat!

328
00:18:37,480 --> 00:18:38,350
I'll come back for it later.

329
00:18:38,350 --> 00:18:40,150
I heard a new restaurant opened.

330
00:18:40,200 --> 00:18:41,440
-Let's go.
-Let's go try it.

331
00:18:41,440 --> 00:18:42,480
-Let's go.
-Let's go.

332
00:18:42,480 --> 00:18:43,480
Enjoy your meal.

333
00:18:43,550 --> 00:18:44,830
Madam, bring me a pot of wine.

334
00:18:44,830 --> 00:18:45,760
Coming right up.

335
00:18:50,750 --> 00:18:51,200
Here.

336
00:18:51,830 --> 00:18:52,750
Here's the wine.

337
00:18:52,750 --> 00:18:54,550
Young Master Wang is here to have a drink.

338
00:18:54,550 --> 00:18:55,880
-Get out!
-Get lost!

339
00:18:57,480 --> 00:18:58,750
Don't leave!

340
00:18:59,160 --> 00:19:00,270
Please don't leave!

341
00:19:00,270 --> 00:19:01,070
You haven't paid yet!

342
00:19:01,070 --> 00:19:02,160
What money?

343
00:19:02,640 --> 00:19:04,680
He is the son of Lord Wang,
the Chief Minister.

344
00:19:04,680 --> 00:19:06,280
You'd better serve him well.

345
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:11,550
So it is you, Young Master Wang.

346
00:19:11,680 --> 00:19:14,270
Please, have a seat. Please.

347
00:19:17,590 --> 00:19:19,790
What would you like to drink,
Young Master Wang?

348
00:19:19,790 --> 00:19:22,400
The best wine you have here, of course.

349
00:19:22,440 --> 00:19:24,270
Okay, I'll bring it right away.

350
00:19:30,110 --> 00:19:31,000
Who goes there?

351
00:19:31,350 --> 00:19:32,640
Young Master Wang
has booked the whole place.

352
00:19:32,640 --> 00:19:33,880
No admittance.

353
00:19:34,270 --> 00:19:35,670
Which Young Master Wang?

354
00:19:35,880 --> 00:19:39,030
The son of Lord Wang Ruhai,
the current Chief Minister.

355
00:19:41,830 --> 00:19:42,510
So what?

356
00:19:43,880 --> 00:19:46,270
It's a misunderstanding.

357
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:48,680
This is my good friend.

358
00:19:48,750 --> 00:19:50,550
She came specifically to see me.

359
00:19:51,270 --> 00:19:52,070
Come here.

360
00:19:55,640 --> 00:19:57,550
Oh, Young Master Wang,

361
00:19:57,550 --> 00:19:59,790
this is the best wine in our restaurant.

362
00:19:59,960 --> 00:20:01,680
Let me pour you a cup.

363
00:20:03,640 --> 00:20:04,680
Let me toast you

364
00:20:04,680 --> 00:20:05,680
to apologize.

365
00:20:06,640 --> 00:20:08,110
Who do you think you are?

366
00:20:08,110 --> 00:20:09,710
How dare you offer me a toast?

367
00:20:12,830 --> 00:20:13,890
Young Master Wang!

368
00:20:14,240 --> 00:20:15,270
Who are you

369
00:20:15,350 --> 00:20:16,510
to dare mess with me?

370
00:20:16,790 --> 00:20:18,520
I am General Xiao's physician.

371
00:20:19,750 --> 00:20:21,880
General, what are you thinking about?

372
00:20:21,880 --> 00:20:22,960
I was just thinking,

373
00:20:22,960 --> 00:20:24,550
if Wang Ruhai's son

374
00:20:24,550 --> 00:20:26,480
is this arrogant and overbearing,

375
00:20:26,830 --> 00:20:28,070
his father

376
00:20:28,880 --> 00:20:30,680
is surely no better at court.

377
00:20:31,640 --> 00:20:33,270
What do you mean?

378
00:20:34,640 --> 00:20:35,480
Lord Xue

379
00:20:35,750 --> 00:20:37,240
might have been coerced.

380
00:20:37,270 --> 00:20:38,270
Coerced?

381
00:20:39,750 --> 00:20:40,920
He must know the inside story.

382
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:41,350
Go.

383
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:47,830
Lord Xue.

384
00:20:51,750 --> 00:20:52,550
Lord Xue.

385
00:20:58,110 --> 00:20:59,640
We are still a step too late.

386
00:20:59,750 --> 00:21:01,030
In broad daylight,

387
00:21:01,030 --> 00:21:02,490
they dared to silence him.

388
00:21:03,070 --> 00:21:03,880
General,

389
00:21:04,350 --> 00:21:07,030
it seems the Han family's case
is not simple.

390
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:11,200
If you let him escape,

391
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:13,000
Lord Zhang will definitely
kill your whole family.

392
00:21:13,000 --> 00:21:13,790
Yes.

393
00:21:14,240 --> 00:21:15,350
Lord Zhang.

394
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:17,270
Zhang Ruizhong.

395
00:21:20,240 --> 00:21:21,880
It hurts! It hurts!

396
00:21:24,000 --> 00:21:25,350
You useless thing,

397
00:21:25,350 --> 00:21:26,680
you only bring me shame.

398
00:21:34,070 --> 00:21:35,000
My Lord,

399
00:21:35,000 --> 00:21:37,480
the young master's hand wound
must stay dry.

400
00:21:37,480 --> 00:21:40,030
He should refrain from
washing his hands for the next few days.

401
00:21:40,030 --> 00:21:41,640
Thank you for your hard work.

402
00:21:41,680 --> 00:21:43,210
You are too polite, My Lord.

403
00:21:43,480 --> 00:21:44,270
I will take my leave.

404
00:21:44,270 --> 00:21:45,070
Hmm.

405
00:21:46,030 --> 00:21:46,510
Please.

406
00:21:46,510 --> 00:21:47,110
Thank you.

407
00:21:52,640 --> 00:21:54,480
What a disgrace.

408
00:21:54,830 --> 00:21:56,070
Next time you cause trouble,

409
00:21:56,070 --> 00:21:57,640
I'll send you to the estate!

410
00:22:01,830 --> 00:22:02,920
Father.

411
00:22:03,270 --> 00:22:04,830
I know I was wrong.

412
00:22:05,270 --> 00:22:06,750
But you can't stand by

413
00:22:06,750 --> 00:22:08,410
and watch your son be bullied.

414
00:22:08,590 --> 00:22:09,590
Advisor.

415
00:22:09,590 --> 00:22:12,000
Find someone to shut down
that restaurant tomorrow.

416
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:12,730
Restaurant?

417
00:22:12,880 --> 00:22:14,880
It's the newly popular restaurant.

418
00:22:15,240 --> 00:22:16,840
The owner's surname is Tang.

419
00:22:16,880 --> 00:22:17,880
She is a woman.

420
00:22:18,830 --> 00:22:19,640
A woman?

421
00:22:19,750 --> 00:22:20,440
My Lord.

422
00:22:20,640 --> 00:22:21,830
If you ask me,

423
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:23,880
this matter is probably not simple.

424
00:22:23,880 --> 00:22:25,210
Think about it, My Lord.

425
00:22:25,480 --> 00:22:26,440
She is just a woman.

426
00:22:26,440 --> 00:22:28,030
How much trouble can she cause?

427
00:22:28,030 --> 00:22:31,160
Ultimately, it's her backer
who is powerful.

428
00:22:31,160 --> 00:22:31,920
Exactly.

429
00:22:32,310 --> 00:22:34,830
That little wench dared to bully me.

430
00:22:35,070 --> 00:22:35,750
I heard

431
00:22:35,880 --> 00:22:37,640
She is Xiao Chi's physician.

432
00:22:38,400 --> 00:22:39,030
Huh?

433
00:22:41,960 --> 00:22:42,960
Xiao Chi?

434
00:22:46,680 --> 00:22:48,880
He just never stops.

435
00:23:09,030 --> 00:23:09,830
My Lord.

436
00:23:10,350 --> 00:23:11,790
The matter is settled.

437
00:23:13,350 --> 00:23:15,270
Xue...

438
00:23:15,880 --> 00:23:18,030
to make you shut up forever,

439
00:23:19,550 --> 00:23:21,550
I had to do this to you.

440
00:23:22,480 --> 00:23:24,310
I have sent Judge Xue's family

441
00:23:24,310 --> 00:23:25,270
out of the city overnight.

442
00:23:25,270 --> 00:23:27,640
Not even the gods can find them.

443
00:23:29,270 --> 00:23:31,680
Did you give them
enough compensation money?

444
00:23:31,680 --> 00:23:33,480
Yes, a lot.

445
00:23:36,640 --> 00:23:39,240
Xue shouldn't have died.

446
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:41,160
But it just so happens

447
00:23:41,510 --> 00:23:43,160
that Xiao Chi found him.

448
00:23:43,680 --> 00:23:45,480
So he had no one else to blame.

449
00:23:46,590 --> 00:23:49,030
My Lord, you are merciful.

450
00:23:49,030 --> 00:23:50,830
Lord Xue's spirit in heaven

451
00:23:50,830 --> 00:23:53,160
will also appreciate your kindness.

452
00:23:55,270 --> 00:23:56,590
However,

453
00:23:56,830 --> 00:23:58,480
that kid Xiao Chi

454
00:23:59,160 --> 00:24:01,640
will probably keep investigating.

455
00:24:02,160 --> 00:24:03,000
Yeah, My Lord,

456
00:24:03,000 --> 00:24:04,790
if he doesn't give up easily,

457
00:24:04,790 --> 00:24:07,190
it really will be a bit difficult
to handle.

458
00:24:08,680 --> 00:24:12,640
You should know
how to handle this kind of thing.

459
00:24:13,720 --> 00:24:15,030
Just leave it to me.

460
00:24:15,680 --> 00:24:16,940
Rest assured, My Lord.

461
00:24:17,790 --> 00:24:18,680
Very good.

462
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:20,880
Go and get your reward.

463
00:24:21,160 --> 00:24:22,440
Thank you, My Lord.

464
00:24:52,640 --> 00:24:53,900
Why did you come alone?

465
00:24:54,880 --> 00:24:55,810
Where is Liu Chu?

466
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:59,030
Recently, the Eldest Princess

467
00:24:59,030 --> 00:25:01,070
has been keeping
His Majesty up all night talking.

468
00:25:01,070 --> 00:25:03,480
He hasn't had any chance
to leave the palace at all.

469
00:25:03,480 --> 00:25:04,550
Useless.

470
00:25:05,640 --> 00:25:08,100
We need patience
to achieve our great cause.

471
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:11,270
Don't worry. If there's a chance,

472
00:25:11,270 --> 00:25:12,590
I'll bring him over right away.

473
00:25:12,590 --> 00:25:14,200
I don't have much time left.

474
00:25:16,550 --> 00:25:17,480
What do you mean?

475
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:20,480
After you left,

476
00:25:20,790 --> 00:25:22,920
the Hall Master developed a Gu poison.

477
00:25:22,960 --> 00:25:25,750
I must complete the mission
to get the antidote.

478
00:25:26,030 --> 00:25:28,290
Otherwise, it's a fate worse than death.

479
00:25:28,960 --> 00:25:30,290
In the King of Mo's eyes,

480
00:25:30,960 --> 00:25:33,420
we are nothing but tools
for his great cause.

481
00:25:34,550 --> 00:25:35,350
Recently,

482
00:25:36,200 --> 00:25:38,930
I've been showing signs
of the poison flaring up.

483
00:25:39,880 --> 00:25:41,240
What about Physician Han?

484
00:25:41,240 --> 00:25:42,900
Why don't you ask her for help?

485
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:46,720
I can't tell her the truth.

486
00:25:47,000 --> 00:25:47,790
Besides,

487
00:25:48,440 --> 00:25:50,040
the antidote to the Gu poison

488
00:25:50,750 --> 00:25:52,810
is only possessed by the Hall Master.

489
00:25:52,880 --> 00:25:53,750
I understand.

490
00:25:54,590 --> 00:25:57,960
I'll hasten Liu Chu's marriage
with the Princess.

491
00:25:58,350 --> 00:25:59,350
Once the mission is completed

492
00:25:59,350 --> 00:26:00,750
and you get the antidote,

493
00:26:02,640 --> 00:26:04,590
just return to Changmo.

494
00:26:15,880 --> 00:26:17,550
I noticed you were coughing today,

495
00:26:17,550 --> 00:26:20,010
so I changed an ingredient
in your medicine.

496
00:27:00,240 --> 00:27:01,200
Well...

497
00:27:02,070 --> 00:27:05,880
I did something very impulsive today.

498
00:27:07,270 --> 00:27:08,030
I know.

499
00:27:10,720 --> 00:27:11,310
You know?

500
00:27:12,030 --> 00:27:13,400
I was there today.

501
00:27:13,680 --> 00:27:15,940
You intimidated all of them by yourself,

502
00:27:16,070 --> 00:27:17,680
so I didn't step in.

503
00:27:18,590 --> 00:27:20,790
Will I cause trouble for Ms. Tang?

504
00:27:21,880 --> 00:27:23,270
Isn't it a bit too late

505
00:27:23,270 --> 00:27:24,640
to say this now?

506
00:27:28,830 --> 00:27:29,560
Don't worry.

507
00:27:29,750 --> 00:27:32,680
If she finds it troublesome,
she'll leave on her own.

508
00:27:32,790 --> 00:27:34,550
You are too heartless.

509
00:27:35,240 --> 00:27:36,270
Me, heartless?

510
00:27:36,550 --> 00:27:38,960
After all, Ms. Tang followed us
all the way from Tianlang Pass

511
00:27:38,960 --> 00:27:40,110
to the capital.

512
00:27:40,270 --> 00:27:41,880
She arranged food and lodging
along the way.

513
00:27:41,880 --> 00:27:43,000
Just for this,

514
00:27:43,880 --> 00:27:45,740
you should show her some concern.

515
00:27:49,200 --> 00:27:51,960
I already had Chengfeng
give her the money.

516
00:27:52,070 --> 00:27:54,470
I don't want to have anything
to do with her.

517
00:27:54,920 --> 00:27:55,720
As for you,

518
00:27:56,790 --> 00:27:57,790
stop showing off.

519
00:27:58,480 --> 00:27:59,640
If something like this happens,

520
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:00,510
who else will take care of it if not me?

521
00:28:00,510 --> 00:28:01,270
Me.

522
00:28:04,030 --> 00:28:06,480
I mean, I'm here in the capital.

523
00:28:06,680 --> 00:28:09,160
If you need anything, you can come to me.

524
00:28:23,830 --> 00:28:24,590
Your Highness.

525
00:28:24,590 --> 00:28:25,270
Jin Xi.

526
00:28:27,030 --> 00:28:28,350
You don't look well.

527
00:28:28,350 --> 00:28:29,550
Are you feeling sick?

528
00:28:30,000 --> 00:28:30,550
No,

529
00:28:30,830 --> 00:28:31,630
it's nothing.

530
00:28:31,830 --> 00:28:32,350
Oh.

531
00:28:32,640 --> 00:28:33,590
That's good.

532
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:40,240
What are you thinking about?

533
00:28:41,830 --> 00:28:42,790
Nothing.

534
00:28:45,550 --> 00:28:46,270
Are you

535
00:28:46,510 --> 00:28:47,640
homesick?

536
00:28:48,110 --> 00:28:48,640
Yes.

537
00:28:49,240 --> 00:28:50,440
I miss my father.

538
00:28:50,960 --> 00:28:53,350
I've never been away from him for so long.

539
00:28:55,270 --> 00:28:58,270
Besides the King of Mo,
is there no one else you miss?

540
00:28:59,200 --> 00:29:01,640
Who else would I miss besides my father?

541
00:29:02,440 --> 00:29:03,590
I can tell you're tired.

542
00:29:03,590 --> 00:29:04,720
You should go to sleep.

543
00:29:04,720 --> 00:29:06,480
I'll rest in a bit too.
